Why Container Deployment ?
It is easily scaled, updated and moved across hosts and clouds.

Container --> Virtualized Network Interfaces
Difficult to have Firewall Rules && IPTables

HOW CAN I DO IT MANUALLY ?
--------------------------
Need you are knowledgeable of ... Linux Networking
No plans for FREQUENT updates of ... Containers + Hosts

1) GOOD Docker Behavior ... Do not OVERWRITE the Host Server Rules 
   -iptables = false

2) Rules you create ... PERSISTENT storage

3) Allow Forwarding ... lo interface, ICMP, docker

4) Add Firewall Rules Incoming, Outgoing, Routing ... Containers Access WEB

5) Load Firewall Rules

6) Allow/ Restrict ICC @ Host ... Inter Container Communication    
   -icc = true


